A container can push directly to a logging system like Elasticsearch however typically you will
    have an intermediary logging agent which is responsible for this task.

Container ─────────> Logging Agent (e.g., Fluentd) ─────> Elasticsearch
     │                                                       │
     │               Log messages (stdout/stderr)            │
     └─────────────────────── Log Forwarding ────────────────┘

